                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-130-off744 t18320105-130-cd745"></join>, 10 panes of glass, value 8s.; 1 handkerchief, value 9d.; 1 basket, value 2d., and 1 shilling
