            . I am a Police-constable. I took the prisoner in Chiswell-street.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I met with an accident in Leadenhall-market, and broke the glass; I told the prosecutor's son of it - he has trusted me with property before, and found me honest.</p>
               <p>THOMAS GROUT. I have known him ten years, and had a good opinion of him.</p>

